data.description: Welcome to this former Model Home largest plan available. Featuring an exquisite 2-story foyer entrance leading to the stunning laminate wood flooring with the perfect mix of carpet throughout the house to create an inviting and warm ambiance.  For those special occasions, the separate dining room provides an ideal setting for "fancy" meals, and if you prefer a more casual dining experience, there's an eating area off the kitchen with island seating.  The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining, allowing your guests to mingle in the spacious living room around the cozy fireplace. If you want to take the gathering outside, the step-down patio, gazebo, and open yard offer a beautiful space with no neighbors behind you, ensuring privacy and serenity.  When the evening winds down, retreat upstairs via the wrought-iron staircase to find four generously sized bedrooms. The primary bedroom features a seating area and his and her walk-in closets, providing ample storage space. The primary bathroom boasts two sinks and a tiled shower with a rain shower head for complete relaxation. The shared full bathroom also offers a rain shower head and an additional hand-held shower head for your convenience.  This is a tech-savvy home with whole house Wifi, ring on the front door, wired for alarm system and an automatic sprinkler system. Since this was a model home, it still retains that model home feel, showcasing its beauty and sophistication.  The full basement is a blank canvas, ready for your personal touch, offering endless possibilities for customization and expansion. The first floor is freshly painted with a new kitchen backsplash. This home is a true gem, combining elegant design, comfort, and functionality. It's the perfect place to create lasting memories with family and friends. Hurry this one is Gorgeous!!
